                "html": "Tritons use a conch shell as a focus to summon aquatic allies. Some specialize in different uses of the conch, such as frightening foes (as the <a aonid=\"110\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>fear</i></a> spell) or using water for attacks (as the spell <a aonid=\"154\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>hydraulic push</i></a>). Triton conch shells in the hands of non-tritons do not produce any magical effects, but have inspired other crafters to build magical <a aonid=\"269\" game-obj=\"Equipment\"><i>triton's conches</i></a>."
            }
