                    "text": "<b>Frequency</b> once per day; <b>Effect</b> The triton blows into a conch shell, casting a 2nd-level <a aonid=\"316\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>summon animal</i></a> spell. The triton can summon only an <a aonid=\"168\" game-obj=\"Traits\">aquatic</a> creature, such as a <a aonid=\"618\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">dolphin</a>, <a aonid=\"143\" game-obj=\"MonsterFamilies\">octopus</a>, <a aonid=\"149\" game-obj=\"MonsterFamilies\">ray</a>, <a aonid=\"807\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">sea snake</a>, or <a aonid=\"174\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">electric eel</a>This creature remains until it is slain, the triton Dismisses it, or the triton summons another ally.",
